2017;;The Resurrection of Gavin Stone;;American;;Dallas Jenkins;;Dallas Jenkins (director); Andrea Gyertson Nasfell (screenplay); Brett Dalton, Anjelah Johnson, Neil Flynn, Shawn Michaels, D. B. Sweeney;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Resurrection_of_Gavin_Stone;;Former child star Gavin Stone is now a washed-up, partied-out man. When he is forced to return home, he pretends to be a Christian so he can portray Jesus in an Easter play being produced by a megachurch.[3]